metadata.name: Fragment
metadata.description:
Zardevor. Fragment. In the center of the arched niche there is a large medallion of solar character, imitating the hosts of heaven. Images of peppers and tumors (amulets) indicate that embroideries of this kind performed a protective and magical role and were hung around the perimeter of the room.

–°oncept author and curator: @sardorbabaev
Artist: @lazizcg
